Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:50.59,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:53.06,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}お祭り野郎と　ときます
